    <date day="09" month="March" year="2020"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes the use of SPRING to setup LSP(s) for
   resilient MPLS ring networks.  It specifies how clockwise and anti-
   clockwise ring SIDs are allocated and signaled using IGP protocol
   extensions, and how such ring SIDs achieve ring protection.</t>
    </abstract>
